{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Ni nokanve dhii agbi tiyi","output":"He could come into the house."}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Wiki nokanve nono gbi difo","output":"The child could walk in the compound."}
{"instruction":"Translate from Balanda to English","input":"Ni nokanve mande gbi njü","output":"He could work in the garden."}
